- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with automated discovery of hypernyms. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper deals with finding the best candidate hypernyms for input concepts or entities. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible category as the paper uses neural networks for the task.
